# Runtime artifacts spawned when bin/cctally-alerts-test runs
# under HOME=<scratch>/<scenario>. The committed per-scenario
# tree is:
#   <scenario>/input.env
#   <scenario>/.gitignore
#   <scenario>/.local/share/cctally/{stats,cache}.db
#   <scenario>/.local/share/cctally/config.json (some scenarios)
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.log
